Excited to announce I’m launching my very own sauce Empire. @smackemsauce Anyone who knows me knows I love sauces. It’s a seafood sauce but you can put it on any dam thing! The BEST seafood sauce! 
Whew Chile I even went as far as importing a unique chili oil found only in Africa & Asia.. y’all are gonna love these dam sauces Soooo GOOD!! BTW y’all know I love a giveaway! I’m giving out $10,000, you’ll be flewed out to LA to meet me! and receive a set of my new signature sauces ! All you have to do is follow @smackemsauce that’s it!!!! They will sell out fast so turn on your notifications! @smackemsauce winner announced 26th!
